name: Blood Cell Detection
shortDescription: This project demonstrates the use of TensorFlow Object Detection API (along with GCP ML Engine) to automatically detect Red Blood Cells (RBCs), White Blood Cells (WBCs), and Platelets in each image taken via microscopic image readings.
longDescription: This project demonstrates the use of TensorFlow Object Detection API (along with GCP ML Engine) to automatically detect Red Blood Cells (RBCs), White Blood Cells (WBCs), and Platelets in each image taken via microscopic image readings.
